COMMON QUESTIONS
Is it safe?

Absolutely. We wouldn’t be doing this if it wasn’t. We have 18 years experience in the dental industry recognised how this simple this process is and felt it could be done by anyone.

If you swallow any of the gel is it completely non-toxic and while we don’t recommend putting it on toast, no harm can come to you.
